### PHASE 02: Gamification Layer (Weeks 7-10)
**Goal:** Addictive learning mechanics
**Dependencies:** Phase 01 complete
**Status:** LARGELY COMPLETE — core gamification systems all built
**Output:** Students engage daily, streaks, achievements

Core Deliverables:
- [x] Daily streak counter — `streak.js` + `streak.css` (7-day calendar, milestones, celebrations)
- [x] Achievement badges — `achievements.js` + `achievements.css` (20+ badges, 4 rarity tiers, dedicated page)
- [x] XP/Level system — `xp.js` + `xp.css` (50 levels, 6 reward types, rank titles)
- [x] Mini-games embedded in lessons:
  - [x] Drag-and-drop labeling
  - [x] Flashcards with spaced repetition
  - [x] Matching games
  - [x] Sequence ordering (bonus — not originally planned)
- [x] Progress dashboard (visual stats) — `dashboard.js` + `dashboard.css` (analytics, charts, recommendations)
- [ ] Study reminders (push notifications) — **not yet implemented**

**Additional Features Built (not originally planned):**
- [x] Interactive diagrams with hotspots (`diagrams.js` + `diagrams.css`)
- [x] Image lightbox with zoom controls
- [x] Glossary term tooltips
- [x] Animated particle diagrams (e.g., diffusion simulations)
- [x] Comparison diagram layouts
- [x] Achievements showcase page (`hsc-biology/achievements.html`)

**Success Criteria:**
- ~~Student opens app 3+ days in a row (streak mechanic working)~~ IMPLEMENTED
- ~~Mini-games load in <2 seconds~~ IMPLEMENTED (vanilla JS, no heavy deps)
- ~~Progress dashboard shows meaningful insights~~ IMPLEMENTED

