## Current Architecture (Actual)

### File Structure
```
/Learn/
├── index.html                          # Homepage (year level selection)
├── assets/
│   ├── css/
│   │   ├── global.css                  # Design tokens & base styles (1595 lines)
│   │   ├── components.css              # Reusable UI components (1388 lines)
│   │   ├── layout.css                  # Grid & layout systems (1847 lines)
│   │   ├── dashboard.css               # Dashboard analytics UI (1024 lines)
│   │   ├── xp.css                      # XP/Level system UI (315 lines)
│   │   ├── streak.css                  # Streak tracking UI (307 lines)
│   │   ├── achievements.css            # Badge system UI (543 lines)
│   │   ├── minigames.css              # Mini-game UI (804 lines)
│   │   └── diagrams.css               # Interactive diagrams UI (629 lines)
│   ├── js/
│   │   ├── main.js                     # Page initialization
│   │   ├── storage.js                  # LocalStorage management
│   │   ├── progress.js                 # Progress tracking
│   │   ├── navigation.js              # Mobile nav & sidebar
│   │   ├── search.js                   # Client-side search
│   │   ├── xp.js                       # XP/Level logic (50 levels)
│   │   ├── streak.js                   # Streak management
│   │   ├── achievements.js            # Badge system (20+ badges)
│   │   ├── dashboard.js              # Dashboard aggregation
│   │   ├── minigames.js              # 4 game types
│   │   ├── diagrams.js               # Interactive diagrams
│   │   ├── service-worker.js          # PWA offline support
│   │   └── lucide.min.js             # Icon library
│   ├── manifest.json                  # PWA manifest
│   └── images/                         # Icons & illustrations
├── hsc-biology/
│   ├── index.html                      # HSC Biology landing (8 modules)
│   ├── dashboard.html                 # Learning analytics dashboard
│   ├── achievements.html              # Achievement showcase
│   ├── module-1-cells/                # 5 lessons
│   ├── module-2-organisation/         # 1 lesson + index
│   ├── module-3-diversity/            # Index only
│   ├── module-4-ecosystems/           # Index only
│   ├── module-5-heredity/             # 1 lesson + index
│   ├── module-6-genetic-change/       # Index only
